":260653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T15:00:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cdad758dcea5dcda161cc16cd71527479f740dd","tid":1237523,"uid":259607,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T15:00:13.000Z","msg":"TVB在反送中報導一事，已經嚴重違反電視通用業務守則中有關「第9章準確、持平及公正」，當中要求「持牌人必須盡一切合理努力，確保新聞、時事節目...的真實資料準確無誤」，以及「持牌人必須確保新聞節目...能夠恰當地持平」，「不可使用謬誤資料或歪曲事實。持牌人亦不應錯誤引導觀眾，以致對節目提及的人士或團體不公平」<br />\n<br />\nTVB在反送中的報導完全扭曲事相，報導嚴重偏袒警方和政府，例如6月12日的「六點半新聞報道」和「晚間新聞」，完全不播放及不提及：<br />\n1. 警方違法向多名記者開槍，棍打記者<br />\n2. 警方違法瞄準市民頭部發射布袋彈和橡膠子彈<br />\n3. 在沒有任何襲擊下，警方違法向婦孺、伯伯開槍<br />\n4. 警方違法向市民投擲鐵枝、磗頭<br />\n5. 隻字不提一些市民向警方掟水樽垃圾等之前，警方在多處在沒有受到任何襲擊，提出任何警告下，違法突然向市民開槍，不斷發射催淚彈，布袋彈和橡膠子彈，導致局勢快速失控<br />\n<br />\n投訴表格：<a href=\"https://apps.coms-auth.hk/apps/broadcasting_complaint/index.aspx?lang=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.coms-auth.hk%2Fapps%2Fbroadcasting_complaint%2Findex.aspx%3Flang%3D2&d=bJSHN4a6RFajNgW6euKvYSKjAP3shAOQj%2BHHIi00eAs%3D&h=d592210d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://apps.coms-auth.hk/apps/broadcasting_complaint/index.aspx?lang=2</a>"},{"pid":"822031e91d07022b06520cd868fc70d1dd0f9ebe","tid":1237523,"uid":260653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T15:00:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c3eeff04cd0dcb5e056dac6134f5d51ae6a85db","tid":1237523,"uid":260653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T15:00:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f4d85b916a16b8bb0f06963f39c437fedf10e0f","tid":1237523,"uid":260653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T15:00:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cafdef773a385c69fef0889eda9355fcdcce3b8","tid":1237523,"uid":186010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid"